description:
&lt;p&gt;HEALTH CARE ASSISTANT&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WINFIELD WARDS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours: 37.5 HOURS PER WEEK&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Winfield Hospital is a fast paced, quality health provider, located on the outskirts of Gloucester.  We are looking for a full time Health Care Assistant, able to work both nights and days on a roster basis. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Joining our dedicated nursing team, the successful candidate will delivery exemplary standards of patient care to both private and NHS patients.  Our 39 bed ward is a busy acute environment dealing with a wide variety of surgical interventions and procedures and medical admissions, both as day case procedures and inpatient stays, and we treat approximately 500 patients a month.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a motivated individual who can join us in the excellent care delivery with which we pride ourselves.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will have up to date experience of working in a hospital environment with ideally a relevant qualification in health care (NVQ 2 or equivalent as a minimum).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of a group of over 30 private hospitals across the UK, as well as 3 neurological units, we are committed to offering a wide range of existing and innovative learning and development opportunities to ensure our staff are engaged to work in different ways to support the changing environment in which we operate and deliver our services across Gloucestershire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are many training opportunities and we proactively support continued staff development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;EMPLOYEE BENEFITS INCLUDE:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• free onsite parking&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• subsidised staff restaurant&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• private healthcare on completion of probationary period&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• life assurance on commencement&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• cycle to work programme&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• discounts programme&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• employee assistance programme&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• long service awards&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• unsocial hours’ enhancement&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;for a full list of benefits, please visit our website&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All offers of employment will be subject to receipt of a satisfactory Enhanced Disclosure Certificate from the Disclosure and Barring Service&lt;/p&gt;
